headline: 1 Restaurant Stock with Exciting Potential and 2 to Think Twice About
summary: From fast food to fine dining, restaurants play a vital societal role. But it’s not all sunshine and rainbows as they’re notoriously hard to run thanks to perishable ingredients, labor shortages, or volatile consumer spending. Unfortunately, these factors have spelled trouble for the industry as it has shed 9.1% over the past six months. This drop was disheartening since the S&P 500 stood firm.
